imdb.plot outline: A talk show interviewing outstanding women from all walks of life and parts of the world who have overcome incredible odds to be where they are today. Messages are positive, uplifting, and intended to provide encouragement to women who are struggling with various challenges. Many are trying to achieve their lifetime dreams of being an artist, while others are facing health issues.
